# Data Models

The application uses Prisma with PostgreSQL. Key models include:

- User - Authentication and user data
- Article - Content management for articles
- Author - Article authors information
- Banner - Site banner content
- Image - Image metadata and storage info

## Schema Overview

- Article model: [schema.prisma](mdc:prisma/schema.prisma)
  - Contains title, slug, content, excerpt fields
  - Related to Author and Image models
  
- Prisma Client: [prisma.ts](mdc:prisma.ts)
  - Used throughout the application for database access